skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Pressed is a digital media company that's changing the way millennials consume media that matters. Our goal is to connect people through intelligent conversations by integrating world issues into everyday life. We make the news easy to understanding by being concise, speaking like your friend, and giving you context on difficult topics. Our first product is a daily email newsletter that tells you what you need to know to start your day, all from a Canadian perspective.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
